name: Beta_lactamase
title: Beta_lactamase
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values includes select antibiotics that are beta-lactams. Including oral and IV formulations.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who are on beta-lactams antibiotics),(Inclusion Criteria: Only use codes that represent beta-lactams antibiotics and any that has the ingredients as Beta_lactams: avibactam, clavulanate (clavulinic acid), durlobactam, relebactam, sulbactam, tazobactam, vaborbactam.),(Exclusion Criteria: Otic, Topical and Ophthalmic formulation)
